    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Next to the Auberge in Satigny]]></title>
    <link href="http://playdegex.github.io/2010/09/next-to-auberge-in-satigny/"/>
    <updated>2010-09-23T08:04:20+02:00</updated>
    <id>http://playdegex.github.io/2010/09/next-to-auberge-in-satigny</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="float: left; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="181" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TJnz4CnuacI/AAAAAAAAzXs/kY9CqkCZNbI/s320/DSCN2558.JPG" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="320" /></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">Playground in Satigny, Switzerland</td><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;"><br /></td></tr></tbody></table>


<p>Adjacent to the <a href="http://www.auberge-de-satigny.ch/">Auberge Communale de Satigny</a> is a public playground and playing field. The climbing frame is brand new and hardly seams to have been used.<br />There&rsquo;s a slide, some swings and a sandpit but the main attraction, while we were there, was playing hide and seek behind the bushes. Some leafy trees provide excellent shade. <br /><br />I expect if you reserved exactly the right table at the Auberge you could just about look over the playground &ndash; I will certainly be back.<br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="float: right; margin-left: 1em; text-align: right;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="264" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TJnz5earGtI/AAAAAAAAzXw/alsCf8_tX7s/s320/DSCN2568.JPG" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="320" /></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">Playground in Satigny, Switzerland</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TJnz5earGtI/AAAAAAAAzXw/alsCf8_tX7s/s1600/DSCN2568.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"></a></div></p>
]]></content>
